description: Zoha is a brand that sells women's clothing at various price points. They offer a wide variety of styles from casual wear to formal attire . You can find everything from winter wear to summer collections featuring materials like lawn khaddar and jacquard . Zoha can also refer to a specific type of outfit particularly in South Asian fashion. It typically consists of three pieces: a kameez (a long tunic) trousers and a dupatta (a scarf) . Fashion trends and styles generally emerge from a combination of factors not a single theory. These influences can include:Cultural preferences: Social norms religious beliefs and local aesthetics can play a role in what people find fashionable.Designers' visions: Creative designers can spark trends with their unique ideas and interpretations. Practical considerations: Climate occasion and comfort all influence what people choose to wear.
